When an online game turns real, trapping its players in its virtual space, the strongest of them, Shin, rises up to put a stop to the madness. But just moments after defeating the games final boss, Origin, and freeing everyone, Shin is transported 500 years into the future of the in-game world. Armed with unrivaled strength, the young swordsman embarks on a legendary journey.
(Source: Crunchyroll)

Guyangcheon betrayed the sect and became a demon under Cheonma. Living as a demon, he committed numerous evil deeds against his will under Cheonma's orders and ended up living a life filled with regret.
The Great Battle of Jeongma started by Cheonma. The long and hellish Great Battle of Jeongma came to an end due to Wisul-ah, who cut down Cheonma, who had even made the three great beings of Jeongpa kneel. Guyangcheon, who had been committing evil deeds as a demon, was captured by Jeongpa and tortured. While passing on information about the Demonic Cult to Wisul-ah with his last remaining conscience, he ended up dying due to Cheonma's prohibition.
However, for some reason, Guyangcheon regresses to the point where he first met Wisul-ah in the past. Realizing that the return was not a dream, Guyangcheon decides to live quietly so as not to do anything he would regret, but for some reason, the people he had bad ties with in his past life start to get entangled one by one, contrary to his intentions.
(Source: KakaoPage, translated)

[Will you join the game?] Giyoung's suddenly thrown into a game of life and death. Not only that but he's also the player with the lowest stats. Still, he's got one skill on his side: the ability to read other players' status! He finds the opportunity of his life when he discovers that Hyunsung is a returner to this world. Now all Giyoung has to do is stick next to Hyunsung and game his way out of this tutorial.
(Source: Tapas)
